basics.name: Timothy Mckenzie
basics.label: Software Engineer
basics.summary: I am a professional software engineer with over 20 years of experience. My experience includes full-stack development, team leadership, architecture, design, and implementation. I have experience working in both government and commercial environments. I have extensive experience in Java and .NET on the server side, and with Angular, React and Node.js on the client side. I also have experience working with Postgres, Redis and MongoDB on the database server. I work well both as part of a team and independently, am a strong communicator and I am always keen to learn and improve.

references.reference: I have worked with Tim on a number of different teams and projects over the past 15 years. He has always been a leader and a very capable engineer who is able to work well in a team and also independently. Tim is one of the most solid engineers that I have had the pleasure of working with.
